  "title": {
   "en": "Souzou Renkinjutsushi wa Jiyuu wo Ouka suru: Kokyou wo Tsuihou saretara, Maou no Ohizamoto de Chouzetsu Kouka no Magic Item Tsukuri-houdai ni Narimashita"
  },
  "altTitles": [
   {
    "en": "The Creation Alchemist Enjoys Freedom -If I Am Exiled From My Hometown, I Can Make Magic Items With Transcendent Effects at the Knees of the Demon Lord-"
   },
   {
    "ja": "創造錬金術師は自由を謳歌する 故郷を追放されたら、魔王のお膝元で超絶効果のマジックアイテム作り放題になりました"
   },
   {
    "en": "A creative alchemist enjoys freedom. After being banished from his hometown, he is now free to create magical items with extraordinary effects at the mercy of the Demon King."
   }
  ],
  "description": {
   "en": "Thor Regus, a boy who lived in the empire, was banished to the territory of the Demon Lord by the hands of his father, the Duke.\n\nThe reason was that he could only use [Alchemy] and didn’t have any combat skills.\n\nThe empire was a military country, and those without combat skills were discriminated against.\n\nThat is why the Empire decided to make him a hostage and sacrifice to the Demon Territory.\n\nThis is a story about an exiled boy who transcends Empires and Heroes and transforms the Demon Territory into a civilised power.",
   "pt-br": "Thor Regus, um garoto que vivia no império, foi banido para o território do Lorde Demônio pelas mãos de seu pai, o Duque.\n\nA razão era que ele só podia usar [Alquimia] e não tinha nenhuma habilidade de combate.\n\nO império era um país militar e aqueles que não tinham habilidades de combate eram discriminados.\n\nÉ por isso que o Império decidiu torná-lo refém e sacrificá-lo ao Território Demoníaco.\n\nEsta é a história de um garoto exilado que transcende Impérios e Heróis e transforma o Território Demoníaco em um poder civilizado."
  },
